entry.title: Wind Advisory issued May 10 at 10:00PM MDT until May 11 at 7:00PM MDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...VERY STRONG SOUTHWEST WINDS SUNDAY... .SOUTHWEST WINDS WILL HOWL ACROSS MUCH OF NORTH AND CENTRAL NEW MEXICO ON SUNDAY WITH GUSTS AS HIGH AS 60 MPH POSSIBLE AS A CORE OF HIGH WINDS ALOFT COMBINE WITH A STRONG SURFACE PRESSURE GRADIENT. BLOWING DUST MAY RESULT IN SIGNIFICANT VISIBILITY RESTRICTIONS. THE STRONGEST WINDS ARE EXPECTED FROM MID DAY UNTIL
